  <brief_title>Study Comparing Tutomesh® Repair to Conventional Surgical Techniques in Potentially Contaminated Hernia Repair and Abdominal Wall Reconstruction</brief_title>
  <acronym>Tutomesh</acronym>
  <official_title>Multicentric Prospective Randomized Study Comparing Technique of Tension-free Repair With Placement of a Bovine Pericardium Bioprosthesis (Tutopatch® and Tutomesh®) to Current Conventional Surgical Techniques in Potentially Contaminated Hernia Repair and Abdominal Wall Reconstruction</official_title>
  <sponsors>
